Source: libwebp
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Yoshimasa Hashida <yoshimasa.hashida@link-u.co.jp>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), autotools-dev, libtool, autoconf, 
 automake, libjpeg-dev, libgif-dev, libpng-dev, 
 libtiff-dev | libtiff4-dev, freeglut3-dev
Standards-Version: 4.1.3
Section: libs
Homepage: https://developers.google.com/speed/webp/

Package: libwebp-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libwebp6 (= ${binary:Version}), libwebpmux3 (= ${binary:Version}),
 libwebpdemux2 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lossy compression of digital photographic images.
 Image Compression format, based on the VP8 codec.
 WebP uses the modern VP8 compression format to deliver efficient
 compression of images for the web. More than 30% extra gain over
 optimized JPEG, for same quality, is not unusual.

